Package org.team1540.rooster.drive.pipeline Description

Collection of useful inputs, processors, and outputs. Contains "stock" or "in-the-box" classes that implement the Input, Processor, and Output interfaces (as well as those interfaces themselves).

Unless otherwise noted, all methods, constructors, etc. in this package throw a NullPointerException if any parameters are null.
